Bxc6 (20... bxc6 $2 21. Ne5 $1 $16) 21. Qf4 d4 22. cxd4 Bd6 23. Qg4 Re8 24. Bd2
h5 25. Qg5 Qxg5 26. Bxg5 Bxf3 27. Bxf5 gxf5 28. gxf3 {white has to be better
in this endgame}) 18. Bd2 (18. h4 $5 {is another of Mickey Adams moves trying
to limit black's activity} Qd6 (18... Be6 $5) (18... b6 $5) (18... a5 $5) 19.
Bd2 Be6 20. Rad1 ({seeing what happened in the game maybe it is better for
white to begin with} 20. Qxd6 Nxd6 (20... Rxd6 21. Nc5 $16) 21. Bxg6 Nc4 22.
Bc1 Bg4 23. Nh2 $14) 20... Qxf4 21. Bxf4 d4 22. Bxf5 Bxb3 23. axb3 gxf5 24.
