Nd4 Bxc5 18. fxg5 $2 Qxg3 19. Rxg3 Bd6 20. Rf3 fxg5 $15 {Black got what he
wanted and is better in this endgame with two bishops and central pawns} 21.
Bxg5 Bd7 22. Re1 e5 23. Rxf8+ Rxf8 24. Nf3 Rf5 25. Be3 Bc6 26. Nh4 Rh5 27. Bf2
d4 28. g4 Rg5 29. Nf5 Rxg4+ 30. Bg3 Bf8 31. cxd4 exd4 32. Ne7+ Kf7 33. Nxc6
